column5: cant believe the crazy buggers up there arent out in their trucks perching on that lol highs in the 20's next week...its time!
Working on truck stabilizers for next year. LOL
No photo today. Pea soup thick fog.

Not a big fan of the new parking lot and they took away the small beach at the fountain. Oh, and it still stinks like a shitie hole. Nice aroma when your out there fishing. How many thousand of tax dollars were spent on the improvements to the lake shore and they STILL HAVE THE STINK.
Only during offshore winds...  hahaha!  The real advantage though, walking with your girl after a romantic dinner you can blame the plant for the 'off-gassing"
